<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <p>Hi {{employee.name}},</p>

  <p>You have <strong>{{documents.pending_count}}</strong> pending documents to submit.</p>

  <p>Please complete them by {{formatDate documents.deadline "DD MMM YYYY"}} to avoid any delays.</p>

  <p><a href="/documents" style="background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">Upload Documents</a></p>

  <p>Regards,<br>{{company.name}} HR Team</p>
</body>
</html>
